data.description: This large 5 bedroom, 2 bath home sits on a 0.79 acre corner lot. The home is approximately 2,547 sq. feet. The roof was replaced in 2020, and the property also features a brand new A/C units and a new water heater. The spacious kitchen has plenty of cabinet space and room for many people to eat and dine. Mostly tile floor throughout, separate laundry room, fireplace and an office/den. This home will be delivered cleared and empty at closing. The property is being sold under appraised value for a quick sale!
